{"body": "I would personally support \"request\" as well, not that my opinion carries any weight either ;-) I don't really care for \"system\" as it seems really generalized to me. \"resources\" sounds feasible, but I feel that the mindshare from \"request\" that rspec has established trumps that. But that's just my opinion, and I'm not even a contributor - just a user! :)\r\n\r\nAll that said, I'll be the *last* person on Earth to complain no matter what it's called!", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/11398641", "created_at": "2012-12-15T01:59:41Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/8307#issuecomment-11398641", "updated_at": "2012-12-15T01:59:41Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 8307, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jaustinhughey/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jaustinhughey/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jaustinhughey/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/jaustinhughey", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jaustinhughey/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/jaustinhughey", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jaustinhughey/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/4411503933352c8b483c98a72516cd8a?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fdb209b9e0e29802256833cb33b36ccb4.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jaustinhughey/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jaustinhughey/received_events", "gravatar_id": "4411503933352c8b483c98a72516cd8a", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jaustinhughey/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "jaustinhughey", "type": "User", "id": 421850, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jaustinhughey/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237f450bd3543c15100a9e7"}, "id": 11398641, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/8307"}
